This option is used to set threshold limit to automatically terminate transaction thread when the CPU is used for certain period of time.

The option value is in milliseconds. To use this option, the value must be greater than 0 and the [enable_cpu_consuming_thread_auto_kill] (./agentHelp? Key = enable_cpu_consuming_thread_auto_kill & type = 1) option value must be set to true.
 
---

* Default : 0
* Type : Number (Millisecond)
* Restart : Not Required
* Related Options 
    * [enable_cpu_consuming_thread_auto_kill](./agentHelp?key=enable_cpu_consuming_thread_auto_kill&type=1)
* Supported Version : 5.3.2.3


